<h2>1. Project Overview</h2>
<p>The <strong>Trade Finance System</strong> is a comprehensive banking application designed to digitize and automate trade finance operations. It features a modern, responsive frontend built with <strong>React & Material UI</strong> and a robust backend powered by <strong>.NET 8 Web API</strong> and <strong>SQL Server</strong>.</p>

